RESPONSIBILITY FOR ANY DAMAGE THAT MAY OCCUR. THE AUTHORS AND COPYRIGHT 
HOLDERS ARE NOT LIABLE FOR ANY HARDWARE DAMAGE, DATA LOSS, OR OTHER 
CONSEQUENCES RESULTING FROM USE OF THIS SOFTWARE.
